    <p>
        This <a target="_blank" href="https://www.syncfusion.com/aspnet-mvc-ui-controls/charts/chart-types/pie-chart">ASP.NET MVC Pie Chart</a> example demonstrates a pie chart for mobile browsers usage statistics. Datalabels show information about the points.
    </p>
